  "title": "PostgreSQL 的多种 JOIN",
  "group": "热身：连接",
  "options": [
    {"text": "JOIN ALL"},
    {"text": "INNER JOIN"},
    {"text": "CROSS JOIN"},
    {"text": "LEFT OUTER JOIN"},
    {"text": "FULL OUTER JOIN"}
  ],
  "objectives": [],
  "questionProse": [
    "哪一个不是 ❌ 有效的 PostgreSQL JOIN 表达式？"
  ],
  "hintsProse": [],
  "explanationProse": [
    "你知道 `CROSS JOIN`，对吧？\n\n    `JOIN ALL` 有没有让你想到另一个操作 `UNION ALL`？\n\n    这里的答案是 `JOIN ALL` ❌。\n\n    正确的 JOIN 类型有：\n    - `INNER JOIN`（默认 JOIN）\n    - `LEFT JOIN`（或 `LEFT OUTER JOIN`）\n    - `RIGHT JOIN`（或 `RIGHT OUTER JOIN`）\n    - `FULL JOIN`（或 `FULL OUTER JOIN`）\n    - `CROSS JOIN`（笛卡尔积，除非后续的 `WHERE` 子句过滤它）"
  ]
}
